media:group.media:title: The Putin shooter
media:group.media:description:
There is a terrible war going on in Europe! At least you can tell which side you are on.

We are two archers from Ukraine and Denmark who decided to do this video together.

Please spread this video, everyone can free use it on all platforms
(Creative Common)

Peaceful greetings
Lars Andersen and Viktoria Diakova

MUSIC: Vans in Japan - Higher Octane
#Shorts

No one was in danger during filming, unlike the real world where people are dying in war right now.
